1a06e911-0f45-45cf-bd30-4388e4932386.do_description: To make the output, you have to...  First copy the input grid.  Look at the lone upper shape, add colored pixels to the pixels lower in the grid such that they are of the same shape and color, even if they have to be proportionally larger or smaller, than the shape in the upper part of the field.
1a06e911-0f45-45cf-bd30-4388e4932386.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input grid.
1a06e911-0f45-45cf-bd30-4388e4932386.see_description: In the input, you should see...a shape composed of pixels in the upper portion of the grid and other pixels lower in the grid

20f22a6e-9bb6-470b-a887-ca776e294d7d.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy exact but make the lower group fill in to look like the shape  at the top.
20f22a6e-9bb6-470b-a887-ca776e294d7d.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same.
20f22a6e-9bb6-470b-a887-ca776e294d7d.see_description: In the input, you should see...a red and blue cross with 2 groups at the bottom

2e7ff8c1-b50e-4410-b86c-bcb1bdd4f4fe.do_description: To make the output, you have to...If you have the same amount of other colored squares, simply copy the pattern. If you have more other color squares, copy the pattern but be sure to fill in more space
2e7ff8c1-b50e-4410-b86c-bcb1bdd4f4fe.grid_description: The output grid size...will be the same as input
2e7ff8c1-b50e-4410-b86c-bcb1bdd4f4fe.see_description: In the input, you should see...two different colors. You will also see one complete pattern.

47e4ca6c-a0cc-43f4-b70e-ab038fc6e58c.do_description: To make the output, you have to....fill in the black squares in between the red squares with the blue squares.  Each red square has one group of blue square
47e4ca6c-a0cc-43f4-b70e-ab038fc6e58c.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input
47e4ca6c-a0cc-43f4-b70e-ab038fc6e58c.see_description: In the input, you should see...a pattern of blue squares and some red squares

fa721c9b-8fd8-4d02-95c3-41ca1226d98c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...add blue color fill to the red blocks to reproduce the upper shape. Leave the red blocks the same size. The new shape can be a different size.
fa721c9b-8fd8-4d02-95c3-41ca1226d98c.grid_description: The output grid size...is not changed
fa721c9b-8fd8-4d02-95c3-41ca1226d98c.see_description: In the input, you should see...some colored patterns. the top pattern is the reference
